<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Mutation-based XSS 방어 버전</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">

  <div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-8 w-full max-w-md space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center">Mutation-based XSS 방어 버전</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">모든 입력을 HTML 이스케이프 처리하여 보정(mutation) 취약점을 방지합니다.</p>

      <form action="/lesson/mutation_xss_secure/render" method="get" class="space-y-4">
        <label class="block text-gray-700">
          HTML 조각:
          <input
            type="text"
            name="frag"
            value="<%= frag %>"
            placeholder="&lt;svg&gt;&lt;script&gt;alert(1)&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;"
            required
            class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded focus:outline-none focus:ring"
          />
        </label>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="w-full py-2 bg-green-600 text-white rounded hover:bg-green-700 transition"
        >
          렌더
        </button>
      </form>

      <p class="mt-4 text-center">
        <a href="/lesson/mutation_xss" class="underline text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800">
          ← 취약 버전으로 돌아가기
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>